mily:等线;font-size:14px\">年</span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">获得清华大学年度教学优秀奖；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 24px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">10. </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">2020年获得疫情防控在线教学优秀教师奖；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 24px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">11. </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">2020年</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">《</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">微积分</span>B(1)》获</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">教育部</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">首批国家级一流本科课程认定</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">（主要成员）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 24px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">12. </span><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">2019年获得清华大学年度教学优秀奖；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 24px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">13. </span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">018</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">年获得</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">北京市</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:等线\">第</span><span style=\"font-family:等线\">2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">届</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">大学生数学竞赛优秀指导教师奖</span><span style=\"font-family:等线;font-size:14px\">；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 24px;vertical-align: baseline;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 等线;font-size: 14px\">14. </span><span styl